## Access Control

### Access Levels

| Level | Who | Permissions | Use Case |
|-------|-----|-------------|----------|
| Public | Anyone | Read-only | Published datasets |
| Restricted | Authenticated users | Read-only | Licensed datasets |
| Team | Project members | Read/write | Active project data |
| Personal | Individual | Full control | Drafts, intermediate work |

### Access Control Checklist

- [ ] Sensitive data is encrypted at rest
- [ ] Access logs are maintained for restricted datasets
- [ ] Data sharing agreements are documented
- [ ] PII is anonymized or pseudonymized before archival
- [ ] Retention policy complies with institutional and legal requirements

---

## Integrity Verification

### Hash Verification

- [ ] SHA-256 hash computed at archival time and stored in metadata
- [ ] Hash verified after transfer to new storage
- [ ] Periodic integrity checks (yearly) for cold/archive tier
- [ ] Hash mismatch triggers alert and investigation

### Backup Strategy

| Tier | Backup Frequency | Copies | Geographic Distribution |
|------|-------------------|--------|------------------------|
| Hot | Daily incremental | 2 | Same region |
| Warm | Weekly | 3 | 2 regions |
| Cold | At archival time | 3 | 2 regions |
| Archive | At archival time | 3+ | 2+ regions, 1 offline |

