## Lifecycle Management

### Data Lifecycle

```
Collect -> Validate -> Process -> Analyze -> Archive -> (Retrieve) -> Delete
  |          |           |          |          |            |            |
  v          v           v          v          v            v            v
 Raw      Checked     Features   Results   Cold store   On-demand    Policy
```

### Lifecycle Checklist

- [ ] Retention period defined for each data class
- [ ] Automated archival pipeline (not manual copy)
- [ ] Deletion is logged and auditable
- [ ] "Do not delete" flag available for data under legal hold
- [ ] Archived data can be retrieved within documented SLA (e.g., < 24 hours for cold)

