## Institutional Repository Integration

### Publishing to Repository

| Repository | Type | DOI Minting | Size Limit |
|-----------|------|-------------|------------|
| Zenodo | General | Yes (automatic) | 50 GB |
| Figshare | General | Yes | 5 TB |
| Dryad | Biodiversity / ecology | Yes | 300 GB |
| HuggingFace Hub | ML datasets/models | No (but versioned) | Unlimited |
| Institutional | University-specific | Varies | Varies |

### Publishing Checklist

- [ ] Metadata is complete (see Required Metadata above)
- [ ] License is selected and compatible with data sources
- [ ] README file included with dataset
- [ ] Example usage code included
- [ ] DOI reserved before publication (for citation in paper)
- [ ] Embargo period set if required by journal
